Evicted Big Brother Naija, BBNaija Lockdown housemate, Wathoni has cried out over threats to her life. Wathoni was evicted from the Lockdown house alongside Tolanibaj and Brighto. Wathoni on Thursday morning opened up about her daily experiences after her exit from the reality show.
The BBNaija star on her Twitter handle revealed that she has been constantly waking up to threats. She wrote: ”Constantly waking up to threats. Thank God say God no be man.” It is not clear why the housemate has been receiving threats as she did not disclose more details.